description: {"blocks":[{"key":"9ujh","text":"This protocol provides step-by-step instructions for downloading publication data from Dimensions, cleaning the data to identify first and last authors, and uploading the data into the Namsor name analysis tool to help determine the gender of authors. {"blocks":[{"key":"12ujc","text":"The export limit in Dimensions varies depending on your subscription. If you are using the free web app, the export limit is 2500 records at a time. {"blocks":[{"key":"9fncb","text":"From the results page, use the Publication Year filter on the left and select a year. {"blocks":[{"key":"1enl0","text":"To export records, click Save / Export to the right of the search box.
